column12: You know, Popola, I understand now why we're twins.
It's because...because we were born without souls.
Devola, I can't stop the bleeding. Oh god, I can't stop it!
This world is too... too lonely for one without a soul. There's too much...emptiness.
Our souls are missing...and yet somehow our tears still work. It's kinda weird.
No! No, I can't be alone!
Stop? Stop? Now you want to stop?
You think you have the luxury to stop?
You cut down my sister like a goddamn animal and now you want to STOP!?
Popola, wait! It doesn't have to—
No one STOPS! It's way too late to STOP!
